---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Recall Notices | Heat & Glo Owner Resources" description="Heat & Glo active and historical recall notices. Confirm whether your unit is affected and what action is required." noIndex={true}>
  <main class="max-w-page mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <p class="uppercase tracking-wide text-sm text-orange-700 font-semibold">Recall Notices</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2">Active and historical recalls.</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-neutral-700 max-w-2xl">If a Heat & Glo product is the subject of a recall, the notice and required action appear here. Check the table against your model number, then act on the recommended action through your authorized dealer.</p>
    </header>
    <section class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-16"><p class="text-sm text-amber-900">Currently no active recall notices. Historical recall actions are archived for transparency. If you cannot find your model and have a safety concern, contact your authorized dealer or the Heat & Glo customer service line at <a href="tel:8884273973" class="underline">888-427-3973</a>.</p></section>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 border-t pt-10"><a href="/owner-resources/" class="underline">Back to owner resources</a></p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
